IPS push base config
--------------------



conf t
hostname IPS
banner motd #STAFF ONLY, GET OUT !#
enable secret callisto
line console 0
logging synchro
password callisto
exit
line vty 0 4
logging synchro
password callisto
login
transport input ssh
exit
service password-encryption
end
wr

